                  <li>‚Ä¢ Ancient Basin (3 fragments)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Bone Forest (2 fragments)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Crystal Peak (2 fragments)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Greymoor (2 fragments)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-purple-900/20 rounded p-3">
