                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Often in hard-to-reach places</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Some require specific abilities</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Check behind every waterfall</li>
